There are three tips in this makefile:

1) .PHONY: clean

It's a rule setted for make to prevent it from doing something with a file named clean

2) clean:
	rm -f $(ODIR)/*.o *~ core $(INCDIR)/*~ 

This two line define the action when typing "make clean" in the shell

3) For more information, visit site:

    http://www.gnu.org/software/make/manual/make.html
